{"tid":2034592,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"終於有動物撚講拎忌廉哥做生意問題","createTime":"2020-05-25T10:19:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T01:27:02.000Z","uid":93014,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cab61d090a8da0543342e5fa4b358343cec42c23","tid":2034592,"uid":93014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:19:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7bO0DYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7bO0DYs.jpg&h=f4e890a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kB5P48.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kB5P48.jpg&h=3d8f1ac8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CSh1op9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCSh1op9.jpg&h=51516719&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Trz7iYw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTrz7iYw.jpg&h=2b0b4e85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下隻貓比人當展品咁放喺度比人影個樣<br />\n隻貓唔識講人話唔想比人摸比人影<br />\n見到佢日日頭Dup Dup 坐喺度唔覺隻貓會好enjoy 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比個藍屍主人當搖錢樹<br />\n死咗都仲要比人摸<br />\n下世搵個好主人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「明星貓忌廉哥榮休，大量貓奴傷感，但小編希望可以藉住呢個平台同大家講下需要留意嘅貓貓照顧之處。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n貓咪本身就喺獨行俠，需要私人空間。貓貓遇到危險時，出自本能會傾向逃跑保命。而紙皮箱一類半密封型地方，就喺貓貓最鍾意嘅避難所。對貓貓嚟講，紙皮箱有兩個特點，就係容易匿埋同埋保暖。貓貓即使親近人類都會想有自己嘅私人空間同時間。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n貓咪除咗需要一個安全感嘅環境之外，另一個天性就是鍾意高空監視位，以便觀察四周環境。記住貓喺野外都喺掠食者同被捕食者，因此只有透過了解環境，先可以搵出潛在威脅，以及覓食。可以嘅話，不妨為貓貓準備一個跳台，比牠可以爬到高處。例如將書架頂層清理好，加上防滑墊，比貓貓隨時都可以安全咁跑到高處。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n除此之外，貓奴都要注意貓貓健康問題。當貓咪脂肪過厚，用力搓揉都摸唔到骨頭，肚子有下垂嘅肉肉果陣，就屬於過胖體型。貓貓體重過重可能引發以下疾病：關節炎、心血管疾病、糖尿病以及呼吸疾病（例如：氣管塌陷）。﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n忌廉哥已經到咗彩虹橋，喺草地度碌嚟碌去，自由自在，無哀傷，無病痛嘅世界。喺現世嘅貓奴們，唔洗傷心，花愛心同時間比其他毛孩啦！﻿<br />\n﻿<br />\n#貓 #貓星人 #貓奴日記 #寵物照顧 #貓貓照顧 #cat #catlife #忌廉哥」<br />\n<br />\nCredit IG: @homiepethk"},{"pid":"25f2467956b0b3ec833922ba692232fb4e778d56","tid":2034592,"uid":93014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"養到咁肥然後話好得意有無諗過隻貓健康呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dLg17YC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdLg17YC.png&h=dc872e9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"60c9dc0c16ae18c541c201445dd1f53a45c377ff","tid":2034592,"uid":93014,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:33:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HpOjUFb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHpOjUFb.png&h=70c05fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「搵唔到佢抬頭嘅相」<br />\n有無諗過隻貓唔想做搖錢樹比人日影夜影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買齊佢啲商品隻貓會開心啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a72b82ab4c6c25c1230c3e3905165034c877049","tid":2034592,"uid":83687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"個仆街主人根本淨係想借忌廉哥搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99bfc1c3271078d905118ed592229a24c0f011e2","tid":2034592,"uid":93014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"9a72b82ab4c6c25c1230c3e3905165034c877049","tid":2034592,"uid":83687,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:40:46.000Z","msg":"個仆街主人根本淨係想借忌廉哥搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T10:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H0hXGpy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH0hXGpy.png&h=8e43cb0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br 