img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"185257dbdf157addc3fdcd1781fcbcc5806ad369","tid":2034592,"uid":93014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBspmFX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBspmFX.jpg&h=f3fd2182&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nF9OOkY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnF9OOkY.jpg&h=384e6a02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個藍屍主人咁樣對隻貓<br />\n隻貓比人圍想走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6893f2f8482a5667e6adfe27f0044dec9dc1a487","tid":2034592,"uid":313630,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:36:35.000Z","msg":"真係愛佢嘅主人會重視佢嘅情緒多於點生財<br />\n有啲位擺明係唔中意 病左仲要搵佢尼搞"},{"pid":"1ed3ce08a73c1ff213ef1d4337d284beeef7a1d0","tid":2034592,"uid":125454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:57:08.000Z","msg":"個主人真係痴撚線"},{"pid":"68d0ddb20d9584c85c98c17da5665a147cadc9c1","tid":2034592,"uid":265702,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"c7414064278d399965c9e5e515378c3b87442336","tid":2034592,"uid":54931,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T11:09:07.000Z","msg":"反觀台灣果個黃阿瑪 人地主人都話驚會嚇到佢地 唔帶佢地去簽名會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:21:12.000Z","msg":"睇忌廉同主人互動<br />\n同埋黃阿瑪同奴才既互動<br />\n就知邊個係愛貓<br />\n邊個當貓係搖錢樹"},{"pid":"cdc6662aacdedd1e63fbbbf48be28e2fd85423cc","tid":2034592,"uid":19178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T12:38:55.000Z","msg":"睇返啲相真係好似好慘"},{"pid":"1a773f74f4cc03c1ac52acf8e08bc5a61b560ab9","tid":2034592,"uid":83687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"770b774a34ede1be3397ae0a1af7c77c5b